{"tid":1016871,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男人可唔可以畀下驚喜人呢 ?","createTime":"2019-02-11T04:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T18:27:41.000Z","uid":119729,"like":6,"dislike":98,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"10f129ff5a9c83db50967d47310c0e7ca023dc9e","tid":1016871,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T04:59:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的,<br />\n上兩個月我生日, 男朋友佢好hea咁求其訂左間餐廳食飯<br />\n無花無蛋糕都算, 食完佢就拿拿臨送我返屋企,<br />\n再同佢D FD打通宵牌.....<br />\n因為咁我黑左佢面兩日<br />\n<br />\n到左今次情人節, 似乎佢都知衰<br />\n晨早就預備好晒所有野, 仲話一定好有驚喜....<br />\n點知尋晚同佢傾電話,<br />\n佢忍唔住一下子將情人節既所有流程,驚喜講晒出黎<br />\n連會送咩禮物畀我都講埋出黎...<br />\n仲叫我讚佢好有心機<br />\n<br />\n真係唔知好嬲定好笑..........<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516c328eb2069cbce0672b2284cebb7bf6aecf93","tid":1016871,"uid":177089,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T05:07:21.000Z","msg":"最後乜都無 surprise<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b974a2148faeedd135ae6cbf54c6af5305c3a9","tid":1016871,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"516c328eb2069cbce0672b2284cebb7bf6aecf93","tid":1016871,"uid":177089,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T05:07:21.000Z","msg":"最後乜都無 surprise<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T05:08:55.000Z","msg":"咁又應該唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢好重視今次情人節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cbf98b2805514f7feaeb30cfb03acf9a5cd8f04","tid":1016871,"uid":20981,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T05:11:23.000Z","msg":"有訂餐廳已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ee9ac8f69746cce8fd3a29df692cad7447dc53","tid":1016871,"uid":119729,"like"